B.Lt=new A.aN(B.aN,"Formation Rule","**Active:** Subject + **verb** + object\n**Passive:** Object + **be** + past participle (+ by + agent)\n\n**Tense mapping:**\n\u2022 Simple Present \u2192 is/are + V3\n\u2022 Simple Past \u2192 was/were + V3\n\u2022 Must/Should \u2192 must/should + be + V3\n\u2022 Has/Have \u2192 has/have + been + V3",null,null,null)
B.bR=new A.ny(2,"examples")
