B.Ll=new A.aN(B.bT,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip",'Vocabulary questions often ask for **synonyms**. Common traps:\n\u2022 "nacelle" \u2260 "fuselage" (nacelle is the engine housing)\n\u2022 "aileron" controls **roll**, not yaw\n\u2022 "elevator" controls **pitch**, not roll\n\nMemory trick: **A**ileron \u2192 **A**xis of roll, **E**levator \u2192 **E**levation (pitch), **R**udder \u2192 **R**otation around yaw axis.',null,null,null)
