B.LA=new A.aN(B.bQ,"What is a NOTAM?","A **NOTAM** (Notice to Air Missions) is an official notice distributed to personnel concerned with flight operations, containing information about the establishment, condition, or change of any aeronautical facility, service, procedure, or hazard.\n\nReading comprehension questions often use NOTAM-style texts or maintenance/inspection documents.",null,null,null)
B.KU=new A.aN(B.aN,"\ud83d\udccb NOTAM Structure",'A NOTAM contains:\n**Q)** \u2014 Subject/condition/traffic codes\n**A)** \u2014 Location (ICAO code)\n**B)** \u2014 Begin date/time\n**C)** \u2014 End date/time\n**E)** \u2014 Full text description\n\nExample structure:\n"A0123/24 NOTAMN\nQ) LTAA/QMRLC/IV/NBO/A/000/999/4059N02858E005\n**A) LTBA B) 2401150600 C) 2401152359**\n**E) RWY 36L/18R CLOSED FOR MAINTENANCE"**',null,null,null)
B.KQ=new A.aN(B.aN,"\ud83d\udd0d Reading Comprehension Strategy",'For any aviation text (NOTAM, report, manual extract):\n1. **Scan first** \u2014 identify the type of document and subject\n2. **Read the question before re-reading** \u2014 know what to look for\n3. **Find key facts** \u2014 dates, locations, restrictions, requirements\n4. **Watch for negatives** \u2014 "not", "except", "unless" change the meaning completely\n5. **Avoid assumptions** \u2014 answer only from the given text',null,null,null)
B.I4=new A.c7("Detailed Inspection (DI) is an intensive examination of a specific item to detect damage, failure or irregularity.","Detayl\u0131 Muayene (DI), hasar, ar\u0131za veya d\xfczensizlikleri tespit etmek i\xe7in belirli bir \xfcr\xfcn\xfcn yo\u011fun incelemesidir.","detect damage, failure or irregularity")
