B.Ld=new A.aN(B.bR,"Emergency Completions",null,B.P0,null,null)
B.KR=new A.aN(B.bT,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Strategy for Completion Questions",'1. Read the **full sentence** \u2014 understand the aviation situation\n2. Identify the **grammatical slot** \u2014 noun? verb? adjective? preposition?\n3. Check **collocations** \u2014 "declare an emergency" not "announce an emergency"\n4. Aviation-specific collocations:\n   \u2022 declare **an emergency** / mayday\n   \u2022 squawk **a code** (7700)\n   \u2022 divert **to** an alternate\n   \u2022 request **immediate** / priority assistance',null,null,null)
